if you want to translate emesene to your language do the following:

* open a terminal 
* cd to emesene
* run xgettext *.py
* open messages.po
* complete the empty strings below the english strings with the translations
* send me the file specifying the language and the abreviation ( i.e: en for english, es for spanish )
* the translations will be in the next release and your name will be added to the translators window in about emesene
